107
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:23,000
On va voir

108
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:25,000
ce qui se passe

109
00:05:25,000 --> 00:05:27,000
si nous avons

110
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:29,000
une fréquence constante.

111
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:35,000
Ça se passe

112
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:37,000
